articles.title: Chromebook Plus is Google's new certification for premium Chromebooks - The Verge
articles.description: Google has announced Chromebook Plus, a new certification that’s similar to Intel’s Evo program for Windows PCs. Chromebooks must have various minimum specs to receive the certification, including 8GB of RAM, 128GB of storage, and a 1080p screen.
